<div class="comment" id="comment-47779702">
  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/Terretta">Terretta</a> 21 minutes ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">Refreshing interconnection of topics.<p>First home “Apple &#x2F;&#x2F;e” was in Africa, using a Korean improvement on the Apple ][+ adding lowercase and memory and more. It was lugged in by Korean ambassador&#x27;s son and remained a better performer than the Apple &#x2F;&#x2F;e once that came out.<p>Once I started looking for the history, I&#x27;ve never found what that Korean machine was.<p>Next came Apple IIc which ran circles around it. Then Fat Mac, SE, SE&#x2F;30… but that&#x27;s a different story.</div>
  
